Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.26,0:00:03.30,Header,,0,0,0,,This is a Gentlemen of the Hàn free fansub.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.62,0:00:06.70,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350,245)\fade(255,0,255,0,1135,4940,6060)}Episode 10
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.25,0:00:06.25,Episode Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(337,404)\fade(255,0,255,0,1135,4940,6060)} Shooting an arrow through a halberd
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sūn Cè fought dozens of\Nsmall and large battles. Eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the 6 commanderies and 81 counties within Jiāngdōng were pacified.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.16,0:00:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Cáo Cāo welcomed Emperor Xiàn of Hàn
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.30,0:00:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and moved the capital to Xǔchāng.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.18,0:00:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He appointed himself Grand General and Marquis of Wǔpíng,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,monopolizing authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Detaining the Emperor, he could send decrees to warlords,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.18,0:00:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,giving him an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Liú Bèi had garrisoned his troops at Xúzhōu and oversees their matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Lǚ Bù, recently defeated, \N has joined them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi had him settle at Xiǎopèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If they were to collaborate \Nand invade me together,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.56,0:00:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,they will surely threaten my position.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.46,0:00:45.50,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(594,355)\fade(255,0,255,0,525,2620,3020)}Cáo Cāo,\NStyled - Mèngdé
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, what plans do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.66,0:00:56.10,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(572,340)\fade(255,0,255,0,440,2040,2420)}Xǔ Chǔ,\NStyled - Zhòngkāng
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll lead 50,000 elite soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.46,0:00:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,lop both their heads off, \Nand offer them to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.18,0:01:03.10,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(581,360)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,1660,1900)}Xún Yù,\NStyled- Wénruò
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,General Xǔ is really valiant!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, this is a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We just established a new capital recently;\Nwe cannot be rash and use force.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Without using a single man, we will end up in a more favorable position.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wénruò, please explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.72,0:01:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Although Liú Bèi governs Xúzhōu now,\Nhe hasn't been appointed through an edict.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.06,0:01:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My Lord, you can petition the Emperor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}to appoint Liú Bèi as Governor of Xúzhōu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Then, just secretly send Liú Bèi a message
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}instructing him to kill Lǚ Bù for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.86,0:01:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}If he succeeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.44,0:01:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}then Liú Bèi no longer has Lǚ Bù to scheme with,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}and thus our plans will work out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}If he doesn't succeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}then Lǚ Bù will surely retaliate and kill Liú Bèi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}This is the 'two tigers competing for food' stratagem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Brilliant plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.28,0:02:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tommorow, I will memorialize\N the Son of Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.40,0:02:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Xuándé!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:42.70,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(112,355)\fade(255,0,255,0,360,1760,2080)}Lǚ Bù,\NStyled - Fèngxiān
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.40,0:02:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you have received an appointment from the imperial court!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.42,0:02:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Fèngxiān, have come to pay his respects!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.56,0:02:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare. I wouldn't dare. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:51.60,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(98,365)}Liú Bèi,\NStyled - Xuándé
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.16,0:02:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't cause mischief! Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.36,0:02:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yìdé, what did I do to you\Nthat makes you want to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Cáo Cāo said you are a wicked man,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and told my Elder Brother to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Xuándé, could it be true that you received that message?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Xuándé!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.36,0:03:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That traitor wants to sow discord;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,he wants us to be at odds!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Have no worries, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.94,0:03:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I vowed to never commit an act of injustice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Virtuous brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wénruò, your 'two tigers competing \Nfor food' stratagem failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.78,0:04:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have another plan called \N'driving the tiger to devour the wolf'.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.44,0:04:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how does this one work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, you may secretly send an envoy to Yuán Shù with a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You only need to tell him that \NLiú Bèi petitioned the imperial court,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.38,0:04:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting to annex the\N southern commanderies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Once Yuán Gōnglù hears of this,\Nhe will surely be enraged and attack Liú Bèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.94,0:04:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, you need to then forge an edict
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,ordering Liú Bèi to attack Yuán Shù.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, once both Yuán and Liú\Nstart attacking each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Lǚ Bù will start planning sedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the plan of\N'driving the tiger to devour the wolf.'
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.96,0:05:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lǚ Bù on one side; Yuán Shù on the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I will observe \Nhow Liú Bèi reacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.58,0:05:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare the soldiers and set a date to march against Yuán Shù.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:44.74,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(105,345)}Sūn Qián,\NStyled- Gōngyòu
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to task someone\N to guard the city first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:47.22,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(107,336)\fade(255,0,255,0,375,1420,1740)}Zhāng Fēi,\NStyled - Yìdé
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother, you won't be\N able to defend this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Firstly, after drinking,\Nyou will become impetuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Secondly, you will abuse the officials.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,When handling affairs\N you won't take advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.18,0:05:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.10,0:06:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless, please let Yuánlóng assist you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.96,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(120,336)\fade(255,0,255,0,415,1260,1620)}Chén Dēng,\NStyled - Yuánlóng
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, my Lord, rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare 30,000 troops\N to march for Nányáng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We leave tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.16,0:06:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He is merely just a mat-weaver\N and sandal maker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he dares lay claim to a major commandery as if he were one of the noble lords.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.98,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(111,336)\fade(255,0,255,0,440,2260,2580)}Yuán Shù,\NStyled- Gōnglù
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.68,0:06:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to attack him, \Nyet he plotted against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How I despise him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:51.18,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(601,350)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,1060,1420)}Jì Líng
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jì Líng!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Dispatch 100,000 troops to Xúzhōu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach that bumpkin Liú Bèi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that there is no turning back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.76,0:07:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,First ordered to kill Lǚ Bù,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,now ordered to attack Yuán Shù!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This Cáo Cāo fellow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He let my Elder Brother be Governor of Xúzhōu,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,but causes trouble for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Before my Elder Brother left, he instructed me to drink less wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.18,0:08:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He fears I will mess up matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I hold this banquet for you fellows to take an oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, everyone will get\N drunk just this one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, starting with myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.40,0:08:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone must quit drinking,\N to guard the city well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something to say first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, you men better drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:46.32,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(100,352)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,1221,1221)}Cáo Bào
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhāng, you may drink, but you can't be so sulky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We were told to kill Lǚ Bù, so let's kill Lǚ Bù!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We were told to fight Yuán Shù, \Nso let's fight Yuán Shù!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it would be better \Nto beat up that Cáo Āmán!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:24.92,Header,,0,0,0,,Note: It was very disrespectful for one to call others by their baby name if they were now an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I wouldn't be sulky anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And he wouldn't be leading my\NElder Brother by the nose anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.58,0:09:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.36,0:09:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,General, I don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.38,0:09:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I never drink alcohol — \NI have a natural aversion to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.52,0:09:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you put this at rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.18,0:09:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A natural aversion? \NA natural aversion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a man of war,\N how can you not drink wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.42,0:10:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a man of war,\N how can you not drink wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to drink just this cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can't drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.58,0:10:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Only one cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm talking about! \NThat's what I'm talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,General, I really can't drink anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.34,0:10:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Rubbish! You just drunk one,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but now you refuse \Nto have another one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I really can't \Ndrink anymore, I mean it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One more! Just one more cup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare disobey my orders?\NThe punishment is 100 strokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhāng, before Lord Xuándé left,\Nwhat did he warn you about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a civil official,\Nso you take care of civil matters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.02,0:11:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you all looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I just say! Take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhāng?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Yìdé, if you saw my son-in-law's face,\Nyou would pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son-in-law?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:12:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's... Lǚ Bù.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I did not mean to have you really beaten,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but you think bringing up \NLǚ Bù will scare me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I want to beat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.62,0:12:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.12,0:12:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Yìdé, you can't beat me! Lord Yìdé, you can't beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhāng!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,General Zhāng!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If it weren't for your wicked son-in-law,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,my Elder Brother would'nt\N have had so much trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat him! Beat him... as if you were beating Lǚ Bù... beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Large-eyed brute! He's \Ngone too far this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:51.30,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(588,335)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,1780,2140)}Chén Gōng,\NStyled - Gōngtái
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,General, we better go at \Nonce and aid Master Cáo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngtái! What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.04,0:13:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Originally, Xiǎopèi was only a place to occupy temporarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that Liú Bèi has left for Huáinán,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,you should seize Xúzhōu while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.04,0:13:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fail to seize it, it will be\N too late for regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Reply to my father-in-law!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him that tonight I will seize Xúzhōu and let him coordinate within!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.24,0:13:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, I want to see how
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that large-eyed brute will \Nexplain his loss to Liú Bèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Jì Líng can retreat to the mouth of the Huáiyīn ad won't dare fight us after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're locked in a stalemate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't you defending Xúzhōu? Why have you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother... Xúzhōu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:14:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.08,0:15:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Xúzhōu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost Xúzhōu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You...! You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, because you told me to follow the decree against my will,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the more I thought about it, the grumpier I got.\NWithout realizing it, I got drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I beat up Lǚ Bù's father-in-law, Cáo Bào,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and he and Lǚ Bù \Ncoordinated from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.44,0:15:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.44,0:15:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, just punish me according to military law!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.02,0:15:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother, what about \Nour sisters-in-law?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They were in the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:15:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Third Brother! Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.34,0:16:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you promise when you wanted to defend the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.80,0:16:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What did Elder Brother warn you about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the city was lost and \Nwith it our sisters-in-laws!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How is this good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As the ancient saying goes:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Brothers are like limbs;
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,wives are like clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Torn clothes can be sewed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you have severed limbs, \Ncan you continue on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.66,0:17:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We three swore an oath\N in the Peach Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we weren't\N born on the same day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:30.14,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(120,335)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,1820,2140)}Guān Yǔ,\NStyled - Yúncháng
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.02,0:17:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,we only ask to die on the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.76,0:17:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Although you lost the city \Nand my family today,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.16,0:17:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,how could I find peace if I let my Younger Brother die early?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Xúzhōu wasn't mine anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When I got it, I wasn't glad. \NNow that I have lost it, I won't be upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Although my family remains within the city,\NLǚ Bù won't harm them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We can still negotiate for their return.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.20,0:18:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Virtuous brother, you made a mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but is it one deserving of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long afterwards, Liú Bèi's camp
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,was raided by Yuán Shù,\N losing most of his army.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,After leaving Xūyí, Liú Bèi wandered vagrant\Nwith no home to return to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,At this time, Chén Gōng offered a plan to Lǚ Bù:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Liú Bèi return and reside in Xiǎopèi to guard Lǚ Bù left and right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.56,0:19:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That way they could make\NLiú Bèi their vanguard in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.76,0:19:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They would conquer Yuán Shù, then Yuán Shào,\Nsweeping through the realm with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lǚ Bù was worried that \NLiú Bèi would be suspicious,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,so he first sent someone to return Ladies Gān and Mí back to Liú Bèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He was very relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi, with his brothers, \Nled his men back to Xúzhōu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.54,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(588,331)}Xúzhōu
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder Brother, I will escort the sisters-in-law back to Xiǎopèi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Help them settle down first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Virtuous brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Virtuous brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:19:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,General.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm most grateful to you for\Nprotecting my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You needn't mention it, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Where's your little sibling?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.64,0:20:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother didn't want to come here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so he took our two sisters-in-law to help them settle down in Xiǎopèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Xuándé,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not that I wanted to take over Xúzhōu— 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only that your little brother got drunk\Nand would hurt someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I feared he would delay important matters, so I rushed to defend the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've returned,\Nyou deserve to have it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've long intended to give Xúzhōu to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.34,0:20:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the right time I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.66,0:20:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Better that it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:20:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm content to live in Xiǎopèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. I'll govern the province for you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.82,0:21:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)} Sūn Cè borrowed my troops for his expedition;
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.34,0:21:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}and now, he already has the entirety of Jiāngdōng.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}He didn't even think to repay my generosity,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}but demands I must return the Jade Seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}This is very detestable!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}What plans should I make to deal with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.78,0:21:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My Lord, Sūn Cè has the\Nnatural barrier of the Yángzǐ River;
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.08,0:21:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}his soldiers are experienced and supplied.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.54,0:22:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Due to this situation,\Nit is hard to find a suitable plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.50,0:22:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Hm? What advice do you have then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.26,0:22:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}We have to eliminate Liú Bèi first,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.24,0:22:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}taking revenge for\Nattacking us yesterday without reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Once we deal with Liú Bèi, \Nwe can attack Sūn Cè; it won't be too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.68,0:22:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Liú Bèi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.68,0:22:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Jì Líng defeated him just now. How could he fight back?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.28,0:22:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Although Liú Bèi has been defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.66,0:22:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}he and Lǚ Bù have reconciled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.30,0:22:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}In addition, Lǚ Bù looms over Xúzhōu. He'll certainly bring trouble in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.84,0:22:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My Lord, please consider these three reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.58,0:22:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}I will first deal with Liú Bèi. \NWhat brilliant plans do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.58,0:22:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My Lord, you may present Lǚ Bù with gifts of gold, silk, and provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.20,0:22:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}This way, he'll have a change of heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}dissuading him from deploying his troops and allowing Liú Bèi to be captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.66,0:22:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My Lord, first get rid of Liú Bèi,\Nthen act against Lǚ Bù afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:23:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Now this will make taking Xúzhōu a really easy task?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.54,0:23:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Not bad... if we first take Xúzhōu and then plot to take Jiāngdōng,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.48,0:23:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Then is it not that the Jade Seal will be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.80,0:23:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.86,0:23:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.62,0:23:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Hán Yìn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.34,0:23:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.12,0:23:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}I order you to send 200,000 carts of millet to Lǚ Bù.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.10,0:23:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Then I will write to him, \Ntelling him not to help Liú Bèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.68,0:23:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Jì Líng!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.10,0:23:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.62,0:23:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I appoint you as Grand General.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.82,0:23:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Léi Bó, Chén Lán!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.26,0:23:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.60,0:23:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are to serve as deputy generals!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.08,0:23:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead 100,000 troops and march the next day towards Xiǎopèi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.44,0:23:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.92,0:23:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.68,0:23:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.80,0:23:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,General, please go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, please, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.86,0:24:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,General Lǚ, no need to see me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.04,0:24:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make a reply to Yuán Shù.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.06,0:24:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I am most grateful \Ntowards him for the grain.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.02,0:24:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't help Liú Bèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.90,0:24:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.32,0:24:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.76,0:24:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiǎopèi only has about 5,000 troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.50,0:24:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we resist \NYuán Shù's 100,000 troops?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.26,0:24:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Yuán Shù so terrifying?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.24,0:24:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just send out your little brother out to fight a few bouts with that Jì Líng!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.56,0:24:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,After that we can talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.46,0:24:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Zhāng, don't be rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.06,0:24:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Xiǎopèi's low supplies and few soldiers\Ncan't resist the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.22,0:24:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you, my Lord, should write a plea for help to Lǚ Bù.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.52,0:24:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How is he going to agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.74,0:25:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngyòu's advice is on point. \NI'll write a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.18,0:25:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}Yuán Shù sent me lots of grain with a letter \Ntelling me not to help Liú Bèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.70,0:25:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}But Liú Bèi sent a plea for help to me \Nrequesting reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.16,0:25:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}Gōngtái.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.64,0:25:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}General, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.30,0:25:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}Liú Bèi is of no threat whilst in Xiǎopèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.52,0:25:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}But if...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.98,0:25:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}if Yuán Shù overcomes Liú Bèi
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.92,0:25:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354.003,438)}and comes to an understanding\Nwith the other lords,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.54,0:25:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}we won't be able to ensure the safety of Xúzhōu.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.68,0:25:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}What you're worried about is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.86,0:25:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}But if you dispatch troops to save Liú Bèi,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.46,0:25:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}you can't account for it before Yuán Shù.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.72,0:26:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}What a dilemma!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.18,0:26:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.30,0:26:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a plan to keep both of them from complaining about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.06,0:26:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome Xuándé!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.42,0:26:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.72,0:26:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare turn down your invitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.90,0:26:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.38,0:26:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.78,0:26:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.96,0:26:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.16,0:27:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.94,0:27:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I've asked you, sir, to come here
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.18,0:27:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to relieve the danger \Nof you being besieged.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.70,0:27:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When you achieve your ambitions some day,\Nplease remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.98,0:27:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well let's —
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.44,0:27:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,General Jì Líng has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.56,0:27:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jì Líng?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.60,0:27:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,General, wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.98,0:27:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Xuándé, don't be alarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.32,0:27:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I've invited both of you \Nhere for a discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.86,0:27:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be suspicious, just be calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.42,0:27:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,General Lǚ has promised \Nnot to help Liú Bèi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.64,0:27:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did he dispatch his troops?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.26,0:27:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't his the intention to help Liú—
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.78,0:28:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,General, could it be that \Nyou want to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.36,0:28:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.64,0:28:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that you want to kill Liú Bèi?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.34,0:28:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.00,0:28:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.06,0:28:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Liú Bèi is like a brother to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.08,0:28:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you are besieging him, so I have come to the rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.34,0:28:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'd better kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.16,0:28:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been a man of war,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.24,0:28:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've always been a mediator.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.66,0:28:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to meditate peace between you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.32,0:28:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, General, but may I ask how?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.60,0:28:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a way—it will\N be settled by Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.86,0:29:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll soon understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.20,0:29:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, take a seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.56,0:29:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,General Lǚ, what are you intending to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.80,0:29:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, come, come!\NLet me introduce you two to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.50,0:29:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've opposed violence for my entire life,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.98,0:29:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,but the entire world thinks I enjoy fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.74,0:29:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a really big misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.24,0:29:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I have prepared a banquet for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.12,0:29:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a good banquet,\Nand it's definitely not a Hóngmén banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.00,0:30:02.50,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: A Hóngmén banquet is a banquet that's really an assassination.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.36,0:29:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to mediate peace between the Liú and Yuán clans.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.62,0:30:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me in the eyes, \Nand please stop this war for my sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.72,0:30:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You two each withdraw your troops and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.46,0:30:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.88,0:30:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.44,0:30:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I received my Lord's order to raise 100,000 well-seasoned soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.44,0:30:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to capture Liú Bèi!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.20,0:30:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure speak big for a dirty lout!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.72,0:30:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You have 100,000 troops. So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.98,0:30:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing you is child's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.94,0:30:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare to threaten my Elder Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.94,0:30:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Third Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.60,0:30:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,sheathe your sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.84,0:30:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see what General Lǚ has to say first.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.86,0:30:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, there will be time\N to go back and fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.50,0:30:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I invited you two to \Ncome here to reconcile!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.88,0:30:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I let you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.52,0:30:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Reconcile?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.56,0:31:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's easier said than done!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.90,0:31:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Jì Líng, you're just an insolent fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.26,0:31:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think I'm afraid of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.18,0:31:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare go out to compete\N with me for 300 bouts?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.24,0:31:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.38,0:31:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.38,0:31:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring my halberd!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.98,0:31:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you two not to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.66,0:31:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now accept Heaven's will!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.70,0:31:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.36,0:32:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}The gate is 150 paces away from us:
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.96,0:32:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}If I shoot my arrow through the center of the halberd-head,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.42,0:32:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}you both shall withdraw your troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.26,0:32:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}If I miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.62,0:32:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}You may return to your camps and prepare to kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.96,0:32:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}Whoever disobeys, I'll send my troops to the other party,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.94,0:32:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}and fight to the death with the offender!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.74,0:32:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}Are you going to shoot...?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.30,0:32:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(347,433)}The center branch of the halberd-head!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.06,0:32:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. I'll comply with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.54,0:32:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I only hope you won't break your word.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.20,0:32:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring the bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.06,0:33:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It is Heaven's will!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.76,0:33:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven bids you to withdraw troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.38,0:33:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.76,0:33:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Serve wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.40,0:33:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's reconciling wine! Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.26,0:33:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,General, I dare not disobey your words,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.46,0:34:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but if I were to withdraw,\Nwill My Lord believe this event?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.28,0:34:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How hard is that? I'll just write a letter to him;
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.40,0:34:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you just simply withdraw.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.88,0:34:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Liú Bèi, am most grateful to you, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.62,0:34:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Without me, you'd be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.26,0:34:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.96,0:34:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you fell for Lǚ Bù's trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.12,0:34:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Lǚ Bù received lots of grain from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.78,0:34:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, this farce of a child\Nwas made to suck up to Liú Bèi!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.30,0:34:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll personally lead a grand army to conquer Liú Bèi and Lǚ Bù!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.66,0:34:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.82,0:34:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That Lǚ Bù is one of the\N most valiant among men;
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.62,0:34:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,he also has the domain of Xúzhōu!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.72,0:34:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If Lǚ Bù allies with\N Liú Bèi from end to end,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.40,0:34:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll be hard to beat them both!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.22,0:34:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't let them off easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.58,0:34:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.32,0:35:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.48,0:35:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.06,0:35:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day, you, sir, \Nsent me some provisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.38,0:35:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now today, you came\N to give me betrothal gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.52,0:35:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.08,0:35:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}General, my Lord has heard that you have a daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.96,0:35:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}and that she is of a similar age to his own son.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.80,0:35:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}My Lord has admired you for a long time and would like a to propose a marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.80,0:35:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}He wants to form a lifelong alliance,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.60,0:35:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}and has sent me here to be the matchmaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.24,0:36:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}What do you think about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.02,0:36:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, please go to the guest room to rest.\NLet me counsel with my advisers — then we'll talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.99,0:36:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.04,0:36:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hán Yìn takes his leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.10,0:36:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be really bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.46,0:36:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think we're all fools in Xúzhōu?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.36,0:36:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.56,0:36:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Who proposed this lousy trick to Your Lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.98,0:36:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}By allying Yuán Shù with Fèngxiān via marriage,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.18,0:36:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}the real purpose is nothing more than to take Liú Xuándé's head, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.22,0:36:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngtái-
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.42,0:36:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How could a simple trick\N ever get past you, Gōngtái?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.16,0:36:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask you keep it secret, Gōngtái.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.38,0:37:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Xuándé is an ambitious \Nhero of this generation,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.64,0:37:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But his feathers have not fully spread yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.06,0:37:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngtái, do you want\N to grow a tiger at Xiǎopèi?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.66,0:37:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, sir. I won't let it leak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.84,0:37:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only afraid that delaying action\Nwill make the scheme obvious to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.04,0:37:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngtái whom are \Nyou referring to by 'others'?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.86,0:37:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that for? I implore you,\N Gōngtái, do tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.60,0:37:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to Fèngxiān
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.80,0:37:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and persuade him to wed his daughter at once. How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.16,0:37:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If this is so, then Lord Yuán will be most grateful to your foresight and virtue!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.08,0:37:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You just wait for good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.12,0:38:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that you have already agreed to join your family with the Yuán's.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.42,0:38:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You've heard about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.78,0:38:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.34,0:38:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.46,0:38:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wonder, when is the big day?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.08,0:38:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The date is yet to be discussed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.92,0:38:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Back then, during the time between the betrothal and wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.46,0:38:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}there are set rules of the duration.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.12,0:38:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}What rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.88,0:38:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}For the Son of Heaven, a year. For the noble lords, half a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.58,0:38:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}For ministers, one season, and for commoners, a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.45,0:39:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Yuán Shù has the god-given Jade Seal in his possession...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.06,0:39:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Sooner or later, he'll declare himself Emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.56,0:39:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Hey! Then do we follow the rules for the Son of Heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.78,0:39:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}That won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.52,0:39:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Then do we follow the rules for the warlords?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.02,0:39:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}That won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.58,0:39:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Then... do we follow the rules for the ministers?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.40,0:39:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}That won't do either.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.42,0:39:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Don't tell me... that we have to follow the rules for the commoners?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.75,0:39:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.58,0:39:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Gōngtái, what are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.94,0:39:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}Many warlords are currently contending for hegemony.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.06,0:39:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}If you unite with Yuán Shù by marriage,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.18,0:39:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}are there not any people that are jealous of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.24,0:40:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}If we select an auspicious day too far off,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.32,0:40:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}then they will take advantage of our wait and lay an ambush on the wedding day.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.32,0:40:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}How would that be good?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.80,0:40:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}So, our plan for the present is that,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.90,0:40:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}although you should've declined but have already consented,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.62,0:40:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}you ought to surprise those unaware warlords
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.62,0:40:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}and send your daughter to Shòuchūn.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.14,0:40:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}You should first rent her a house there,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.40,0:40:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}then select an auspicious day for the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.80,0:40:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(345,430)}This way, you can be safe with no risk at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.04,0:40:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gōngtái, you're absolutely right. \NI'll make the preparations right away!
